What Users Need to Integrate

They need:

1. API key
2. User ID
3. Endpoint URL
4. Chatbot message
5. Optional metadata

Example metadata:

{
  "userId": "user_123",
  "message": "Write a follow-up email",
  "metadata": {
    "app": "sales_copilot",
    "team": "sales",
    "role": "account_executive"
  }
}
Security Requirements

For enterprise integration, include:

API keys
OAuth / SSO
Tenant isolation
Encryption at rest
Encryption in transit
Role-based access
Audit logs
Memory delete controls
Privacy Controls Users Must Have

Every integrated system should show:

View memory
Edit memory
Delete memory
Pause memory
Private mode
